+# Handoff: Plan-mode TTY suspension fix verification complete
+
+## Status
+
+Verification of the `seher plan` TTY-suspension fix is complete. All requirements from `/Users/takumi/.local/share/cruise/sessions/20260625101833293_66edf215f19b495fa6c9ce7083c6e3ac/plan.md` are implemented and no code changes were required.
+
+## What was done
+
+- Ran `cargo clippy --all-features --all-targets` -> clean (no warnings).
+- Ran `cargo test -p seher-cli` -> 43 passed, 0 failed.
+- Ran `cargo test -p seher-sdk` -> 167 passed, 0 failed.
+- Ran `cargo test --all` -> all passed.
+- Manually ran `./target/debug/seher plan hello` in the agent harness (non-foreground / no TTY):
+  - Got explicit error `cannot open controlling terminal /dev/tty: Device not configured (os error 6)` and exit code 1.
+  - Confirmed no `zsh: suspended (tty output)` occurs.
+- Verified source files implement the plan:
+  - `crates/seher-cli/src/stream.rs`: `StreamOutput` enum with `Stdout`/`CaptureOnly`, `drain_stream`, `drain_to_capture`.
+  - `crates/seher-cli/src/prompt.rs`: `ensure_editor_available()` foreground check via `tcgetpgrp`/`getpgrp`, `/dev/tty` editor stdio.
+  - `crates/seher-cli/src/mode_plan.rs`: plan generation uses `CaptureOnly`, build phase uses `Stdout`.
+  - `crates/seher-cli/src/mode_build.rs`: build mode uses `Stdout`.
+  - `crates/seher-cli/src/run_mode.rs`: output policy threaded through `resolve_and_stream`/`stream_with_http_retry`.
+  - `README.md`: plan-mode description updated (lines 59-60, 113-114).
+- Used `agent-browser` to view a local verification report and then closed it.
+- Stopped the temporary local HTTP server used to serve the report.
+
+## What remains
+
+Nothing blocking. Optional follow-ups:
+
+1. (Optional) In a real foreground macOS/Linux terminal, run `EDITOR=true seher plan hello` to confirm the editor opens and the plan is not pre-dumped to stdout. This cannot be fully exercised inside the agent harness because `/dev/tty` is not available here.
+2. (Optional) Merge the branch once the above manual check is satisfied.
+
+## Next-agent starting position
+
+1. Branch is at commit `a3a29ca` (after `bb2b6b8` plan-mode fix + ASCII compliance pass).
+2. No code changes are pending; `git status` shows only this `.handoff.md` file untracked.
+3. If desired, run the optional foreground-terminal manual test and merge.
